Name: Government Service
Description: A service provided by a government to citizens and businesses. The government entity can be at any level (e.g municipal, regional, national).

Properties.Name: Government service channel
Properties.Description: A channel for accessing the service. (e.g. a website, a telephone number, or a physical location.)

Properties.Name: Issues permit
Properties.Description: A permit type that is issued through the service.

Properties.Name: Operating organization
Properties.Description: An organization that operates the service on behalf of the agency.

Properties.Name: Providing agency
Properties.Description: The government agency that provides or sponsors the service.
